31. Qh4 Be3+ 32. Kh1 Rf1# {0-1 (32) Solak,D (2629) -Djukic,N (2523) Batumi 2018} 
) Nxe2+ 14. Nxe2 Ne5 $146 ({It is very important to note, not to play the most 'logical'}14... 
